<h1>Newsstand</h1>
<h2>Welcome, <%=@user.name.capitalize %></h2>
<h3>Thank you for your interest in Newsstand. We source the best reading materials for smart people like you.</h3>
<h3>Please select your subscription type:</h3>

<form action="/show" method="POST">
<%@subscription_levels.each do |subscription|%>
    <input type="checkbox" name=subscription></input><br></br>
    <%=current_user.subscription_ids << subscription%>
<%end%>
<br> </br>
<input type="submit" value="Confirm subscription">
</form>
<br>

<h3>Learn more about each level:</h3><br>

<h3><a href="/subscriptions/lite">LITE</a></h3>
<p>Just the basic titles in news and entertainment. Five titles, $9.99/month</p><br>
<h3><a href="/subscriptions/extra">EXTRA</a></h3>
<p>Are you into yachts? Or perhaps cigars? Get the basics with a touch of flair. Twelve titles, $15.99/month</p><br>
<h3><a href="/subscriptions/everything">EVERYTHING</a></h3>
<p>If you consider yourself to be the ultimate consumer of the zeitgeist, this is the deal for you. Unlimited titles, unlimited categories, only $19.99/month</p><br>

<a href="/titles">Titles</a>
<a href="/logout">Logout</a>


